Class Summary
Card This class encapsulates the basic behaviors and characteristics of a standard playing card.
CardSuit Objects of this class can be used to represent the suits for standard playing cards (SPADES, HEARTS, DIAMONDS, CLUBS).
CardValue Objects of this class can be used to represent the values for standard playing cards (JOKER, ACE through KING).
Deck This class encapsulates the basic behaviors and characteristics of a standard deck of playing cards.
DeckTester Used to test the functionality of the card game classes.
